issue.title: Infinite loop on `annotate classes` with custom App\Model\Table\Table class
issue.body:
What i did:
1) Created new project from cakephp/app
2) Installed following plugins:
```
friendsofcake/search
dereuromark/cakephp-setup
dereuromark/cakephp-tools
dereuromark/cakephp-ide-helper
```
3) Created custom App\Model\Table\Table class:
```php
namespace App\Model\Table;

use Tools\Model\Table\Table as ToolsTable;

class Table extends ToolsTable
{
    public function initialize(array $config): void
    {
        parent::initialize($config);

        $this->addBehavior('Search.Search');
        $this->addBehavior('Shim.Nullable');
    }
}
```
4) baked my models with
```
bin/cake bake model all --theme=Setup
```
so they all extend my `\App\Model\Table\Table`

5) then called `bin/cake annotate all`

```

[Controllers]

[Shells]

[Commands]

[View]
/src/View
 -> AppView.php
```
